title: Gmail API List History Operation Response Schema
description: Schema representing the output of the List History operation in Gmail API

history.description: List of history records. Any `messages` contained in the response will typically only have `id` and `threadId` fields populated.

historyId.description: The ID of the mailbox's current history record.

nextPageToken.description: Page token to retrieve the next page of results in the list.

statusCode.description: HTTP status code of the API response.

headers.description: HTTP headers of the API response.
